---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = "2 June 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions — Australian Tax Calculator"
  description="Terms and conditions for using the Australian Tax Calculator website."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </Fragment>

  <main class="container">

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
      <p>
        Please read these Terms and Conditions carefully before using the Australian Tax Calculator
        website. By accessing or using this site, you agree to be bound by these terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>1. General Information Only</h3>
      <p>
        The Australian Tax Calculator is a free estimation tool designed to provide <strong>general
        information only</strong>. It is not a substitute for professional financial, tax, or legal
        advice. The results produced by this calculator are estimates based on publicly available ATO
        tax rates and should not be relied upon for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Lodging a tax return</li>
        <li>Making investment or superannuation decisions</li>
        <li>Negotiating salary or employment contracts</li>
        <li>Any other formal financial or legal purpose</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For personalised advice, consult a registered tax agent, financial adviser, or the
        Australian Taxation Office directly at <a href="https://www.ato.gov.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ato.gov.au</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>2. Accuracy of Information</h3>
      <p>
        While we make every effort to keep tax rates, thresholds, and offsets up to date, we do not
        guarantee that the information is complete, current, or free from errors. Tax legislation
        can change, and the ATO may update rates, thresholds, or interpretation at any time.
      </p>
      <p>
        The calculator does not account for all individual circumstances, including but not limited
        to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>The Medicare Levy Surcharge (based on private hospital cover)</li>
        <li>The Senior Australians and Pensioners Tax Offset (SAPTO)</li>
        <li>Investment income, capital gains, or rental income</li>
        <li>Foreign income or foreign tax credits</li>
        <li>Trust distributions or partnership income</li>
        <li>Family tax benefits</li>
        <li>State or territory taxes and levies</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>3. No Tax Agent Relationship</h3>
      <p>
        Use of this website does not create a tax agent, financial adviser, or any professional
        relationship between you and the owners of this site. We are not registered tax agents
        under the <em>Tax Agent Services Act 2009</em> and do not provide tax agent services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>4. Limitation of Liability</h3>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by Australian law, we exclude all liability for any loss
        or damage (including direct, indirect, or consequential loss) arising from your use of or
        reliance on this website or the information it contains. This includes but is not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Errors or inaccuracies in tax calculations</li>
        <li>Interruptions or unavailability of the site</li>
        <li>Decisions made based on calculator results</li>
        <li>Any tax liability, penalty, or interest arising from reliance on this tool</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>5. Intellectual Property</h3>
      <p>
        All content on this site — including text, code, design, and graphics — is the property of
        the Australian Tax Calculator and is protected by Australian copyright law. You may view and
        use the content for personal, non-commercial purposes. You may not reproduce, republish, or
        distribute content without prior written permission.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>6. Third-Party Links and Advertising</h3>
      <p>
        This site displays advertisements served by Google AdSense and may contain links to
        third-party websites. We do not endorse and are not responsible for the content, accuracy,
        or privacy practices of any linked or advertised sites.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>7. Governing Law</h3>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of Australia. Any disputes arising from your use of
        this website will be subject to the jurisdiction of the courts of Australia.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>8. Changes to These Terms</h3>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to update these Terms and Conditions at any time. The "Last updated"
        date at the top of this page indicates when the most recent changes were made. Continued use
        of the site after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>9. Contact</h3>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about these Terms, please use our <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="back-link">
      <a href="/">&larr; Back to the calculator</a>
    </div>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  main {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius, 12px);
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow, 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08));
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--au-navy, #00205b);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--au-navy, #00205b);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--au-gold, #ffcd00);
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
  }

  p, li {
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--au-navy, #00205b);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .meta {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    padding: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .back-link a {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back-link a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .card { padding: 1.25rem 1rem; }
  }
</style>
